</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Tobacco tax gap </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">estimates 2012/13</span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">. HMRC, October 2013</span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">&amp; information provided by HMRC</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Office for National Statistics website, 2013</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Department for Transport website, 2013</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Progress in tackling tobacco </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">smuggling.</span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> National Audit Office, June 2013 &amp; previously published data</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">Written Answer. Hansard, 10 June 2013 38W</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Tackling tobacco smuggling. Quarter 1 outputs (April to June 2013)</span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt">. HMRC, 2013</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Dundee tobacco factory sees three arrested after </span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">raid.</span><span style="color:#122632; font-family:Arial; font-size:9pt"> BBC News, 27 September 2012</span></h2><h2 style="font-weight:normal; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="color:#122632; font-family:'MS PGothic'; font-size:9pt">・</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;